  <h2>Rocket Jump Zone Servers</h2>
  <p>If you compete in our tournaments then it's recommended to practice in our servers as we use a different game balance.<br>
    Name changing in our servers is forbidden. Don't play stalker.</p>
  <h3>Main differences from XPM:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Crylink weapon is replaced with a modified Arc weapon</li>
    <li>MachineGun has no reload, only 1 magazine 60 bullets</li>
    <li>Blaster weapon has now a secondary (dmg 1, force:3, refire 0.2)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Issues</h3>

  <p>It could happen that somebody left a non official balance config on the server, fix it with:&nbsp;&nbsp; <kbd>vcall balance-default</kbd></p>

