  <h2>Config / Console</h2>
  <p>press "~" or "shift + esc" to open the console</p>
  <ul>
    <li>There are 2 pre-made configs:<br>
      <span style="border-bottom:1px groove" data-preview-image="../../images/ch1mpnotic/player-preview.jpg">Competitive (default)</span>&nbsp;
      <kbd>exec player.cfg</kbd>&nbsp; (textures off, simple items (2D), HUD, reduced effects..)<br>
      <span style="border-bottom:1px groove" data-preview-image="../../images/ch1mpnotic/caster-preview.jpg">Caster</span>&nbsp;
      <kbd>exec caster.cfg</kbd>&nbsp; (texturees on, normal items (3D), HUD, eye candy..)</li>
    <li>If you prefer male announcer: &nbsp;<kbd>cl_announcer male</kbd>
    </li>

    <li>In game vote / call commands:
      <b>vcall chmap map</b>
      (vote for a diff map),
      <b>vcall endmatch</b>
      (call a gg, end match)<br>
      <b>vcall restart</b>
      (restart current map),
      <b>vcall nextmap</b>
      (vote for a next map)</li>
    <li>
      <u>more useful commands:</u><br>
      "vcall cointoss" - heads or tails?<br>
      "vcall bots", "vcall nobots" - who needs bots? our playerbase is huge<br>
      "lsmaps" - print names of all available maps<br>
      "timeout", "timein" - pause and unpause the game<br>
      <u>shortcuts:</u><br>
      "q" - quit, "d" - disconnect, "s" - spec, "r" - ready<br>
    </li>

    <li>
      <u>more tuning commands:</u>
      (vid_restart might be needed)<br>
      <kbd>gl_picmip_world 0</kbd>&nbsp; turn textures on<br>
      you can reduse effects:<br>
      <kbd>cl_particles_alpha 0.2</kbd><br>
      <kbd>cl_particles_sparks 0</kbd><br>
      <kbd>cl_particles_blood 0</kbd><br>
      <kbd>cl_gentle_gibs 1</kbd><br>
      <kbd>r_coronas 0</kbd><br>

      if you have low FPS (probably in caster mode) then try:<br>
      <kbd>exec effects-high.cfg</kbd>&nbsp; or &nbsp;<kbd>exec effects-normal.cfg</kbd>
    </li>
  </ul>

